Class VersionFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.diachron.detection.complex_change.VersionFilter

  • public class VersionFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a Version Filter which is essentially an RDF triple which has a specific presence Presence on either the old or new version.
